Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强者出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}从今天起我最酷
